<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>Taleem</title>

<style>

body{
  margin:0;
  font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
  background:#f5f6f7;
  color:#222;
}

.wrapper{
  max-width:1100px;
  margin:auto;
  padding:35px 20px;
}

/* HERO HEADER */

.hero{
  background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1c6fb8,#0f4f8a);
  color:white;
  text-align:center;
  padding:55px 20px 60px 20px;
  margin-bottom:35px;
  box-shadow:0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
}

.hero h1{
  margin:0;
  font-size:38px;
  letter-spacing:0.5px;
}

/* posters */

.posters{
  display:flex;
  gap:30px;
  margin-bottom:25px;
}

.poster{
  flex:1;
  display:block;
  border-radius:10px;
  overflow:hidden;
  border:3px solid transparent;
  transition:all 0.35s ease;
}

/* image */

.poster img{
  width:100%;
  display:block;
  transition:transform 0.35s ease;
  box-shadow:0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
}

/* HOVER EFFECT */

.poster:hover{
  transform:translateY(-6px);
  border:3px solid #1bb6b2;
  box-shadow:0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
  cursor:pointer;
}

.poster:hover img{
  transform:scale(1.04);
}

/* divider under posters */

.poster-divider{
  width:120px;
  height:3px;
  background:linear-gradient(90deg,#1c6fb8,#1bb6b2);
  margin:10px auto 30px auto;
  border-radius:3px;
}

/* stacked on small screens */

@media (max-width:900px){

.posters{
  flex-direction:column;
}

}

/* text section */

.info{
  max-width:800px;
  margin:auto;
  line-height:1.7;
  font-size:16px;
  color:#444;
}

.info p{
  margin-bottom:18px;
}

/* footer */

footer{
  margin-top:60px;
  padding:25px;
  text-align:center;
  font-size:14px;
  color:#777;
  border-top:1px solid #ddd;
}

.stats-bar{
  display:flex;
  justify-content:space-around;
  align-items:center;
  gap:20px;
  padding:30px 20px;
  margin:20px 0 40px 0;
  background:white;
  border-radius:10px;
  box-shadow:0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
}

.stat{
  text-align:center;
}

.stat-number{
  font-size:28px;
  font-weight:bold;
  color:#1c6fb8;
}

.stat-label{
  font-size:14px;
  color:#666;
  margin-top:6px;
}
</style>

</head>

<body>

<header class="hero">
<h1>Taleem.Help Online Courses</h1>
</header>

<div class="wrapper">

<!-- posters -->

<div class="posters">

<a class="poster" href="/class8">
<img src="/images/fbise8math-poster.png">
</a>

<a class="poster" href="/class9">
<img src="/images/fbise9math-poster.png">
</a>

</div>

<%- include('./stats') %>

<!-- explanation text -->

<div class="info">

<p>
Our online mathematics classes are designed for students studying under the Federal Board. 
The lessons focus on clear explanations, visual understanding, and step-by-step problem solving 
so that students can build strong mathematical foundations rather than relying on memorization.
</p>

<p>
Each topic is taught using carefully prepared visual material that helps students understand 
concepts in algebra, geometry, and other core areas of mathematics. The goal is to make learning 
calm, structured, and easy to follow for students who want clarity in their studies.
</p>

<p>
Students can choose their class and begin exploring the chapters immediately. 
Every lesson is prepared to support exam preparation while also strengthening 
conceptual understanding of mathematics.
</p>

</div>

</div>

<footer>

© 2026 Taleem.help — Online Mathematics Learning

</footer>

</body>
</html>